    dc:creator "Riyanto, Awal; Mcguire, Jimmy A.; Kusrini, Mirza D.; Basyir, Irfan Haidar; Kaiser, Hinrich" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "A new small bent-toed gecko of the genus Cyrtodactylus (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from the lower slopes of Mount Tambora, Sumbawa Island, Indonesia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.376944>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.376945>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.376946>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.376947>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.376948> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.376944>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Photographs in life of Cyrtodactylus tambora sp. nov. from the northern slopes of Mount Tambora, Sumbawa Island, Indonesia. (A) The holotype, an adult male (MZB. Lace. 13298). (B) A subadult male paratype (MZB. Lace. 13296). (C) The female paratype, gravid with two eggs (MZB. Lace. 13297). Photograph by A. Riyanto." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/376944/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.376945>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Comparison of chin shields for the six known Cyrtodactylus species from the Lesser Sunda Islands. (A) Cyrtodactylus tambora sp. nov., holotype, MZB. Lace. 13298. (B) C. celatus, holotype, BMNH 1926.10. 30.45. (C) C. laevigatus, FLMNH 28911. (D) C. darmandvillei, lectotype, ZMA 10943. (E) C. gordongekkoi, paratype, ZRC 2.3381. (F) C. wetariensis, holotype, AMNH 32165. Photograph by A. Riyanto (A) and H. Kaiser (B – F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/376945/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.376946>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Precloacal and femoral region of the holotype of Cyrtodactylus tambora sp. nov. (MZB. Lace. 13298), showing the arrangement of precloacal pores that four pores situated in a short groove, and enlarged precloacofemoral scales. Photograph by A. Riyanto." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/376946/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.376947>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Map of the Lesser Sunda Islands showing the positions of the Inner and Outer Banda Arcs as well as the type localities of Cyrtodactylus endemic to this archipelago. Map modified from Kathriner et al. 2014." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/376947/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.376948>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Habitat of Cyrtodactylus tambora sp. nov. along the riverbank of the Oi Marai River, Sumbawa Island, Indonesia. Photograph by A. Riyanto." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/376948/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

